    public abstract class AbstractPrimitiveLeafNodeBuilder
extends AbstractLeafNodeBuilder
    Abstract class that implements the createInfoNode(Object, String) for classes that are leaves in the semantic model, and also primitive types or wrappers.

        public InfoNode createInfoNode(java.lang.Object object,
                      java.lang.String persistName)
        Description copied from interface: NodeBuilder
        Generates an InfoNode from the specified Object. This method is used for objects that have an overriding node builder and are not contained within a class. For example, suppose you would like to persist an ArrayList for serialization and would like to maintain the type information.
